{"tid":1092689,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"王者再臨 Motorola發佈超薄大熒幕摺機","createTime":"2019-04-05T05:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T16:32:53.000Z","uid":77956,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"de0d9b8fc8b7ec2e337f6ad484c20feb743f1fea","tid":1092689,"uid":77956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"在多年前的MicroTAC以後，摺機世界一直沒有夠份量的新力軍。就在年初，摩托羅拉在北美宣佈摺機家族的重量級新成員&mdash;Star tac。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b3/MotorolaStarTAC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fb3%2FMotorolaStarTAC.jpg&h=14eff708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nStar tac輕巧非常，只重94g，機身雖小卻有劃時代的功能。機身搭配了一塊大大的LED螢幕，且具有最新的SMS功能，能傳送文字訊息。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://cdn.slashgear.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/motorola_startac_nostalgia_0-580x418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fcdn.slashgear.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F07%2Fmotorola_startac_nostalgia_0-580x418.jpg&h=cce07dc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外，此機亦有獨一無二的震動功能，讓你在無聲無息中知會電話的到來。多元的功能表，讓你隨心、快捷的選擇各項功能，機側更設智慧鍵，讓你一按即達通訊錄，無需從目錄選單進入。大膽採用了最新式的lithium-ion鋰電池，不必再受電池記憶放應的困擾。 <br />\n<br />\n本機在一月已於美國上市，單機售價約$1,000美金。"},{"pid":"c0bf30a2e016923981cfd05a5f8700b2fdbe0819","tid":1092689,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:34:16.000Z","msg":"razr M巾"},{"pid":"3aa256e401c8009604b4b06f84fbfa4e4f9b0923","tid":1092689,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T14:38:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7dbfd9271105aebd35a1563f629912fd99d0b4c","tid":1092689,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />型"},{"pid":"d11dc34945aceda4930